               type="paratext"><subst><del>Eingelangt</del> <add>exped.</add></subst> am 18. DEZ. 1922<lb
                  xml:id="uuid_befa499e-eb12-4862-a269-47608bf1dba2"/>r.m.R. K.</note>
         </p>
